<br>
Year__Revenues___Outlays<br>
2000__2,025.2____1,788.8  <br>
2001__1,991.2____1,863.8         <br>
2002__1,853.2____2,011.0          <br>
2003__1,782.3____2,157.6          <br>
Denominated in billions of dollars                           <br>
